  <brief_title>Primary Care iSBIRT to Reduce Serious Teen Health Risks</brief_title>
  <official_title>Primary Care Internet/Intranet-based Screening, Brief Intervention, and Referral to Treatment (iSBIRT) System to Reduce Serious Teen Health Risks</official_title>
  <sponsors>
